Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&Hffffff\c&Hff&\fn楷体\b1\fs16}《社长的秘书是个痴女》\N{\3c&H00\c&Hffffff&\fn楷体\fs12\b1}（桐嵨莉乃)\N{\fntimes new roman\fs8\b1}BF-516\N{\c&H3ee0fd&\fs8\fn宋体}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.53,0:00:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传到制作公司的一封电子邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.01,0:00:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,制作公司商谈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.94,0:00:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个内容是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.41,0:00:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉突然打扰 我是X IT公司的员工\N突然发现老板和秘书的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.62,0:00:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,性招待事件影片 秘昼很性感\N公司员工都很喜欢她
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.16,0:00:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是最近这影片在公司内传开了\N所以想把影片给贵公司
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.11,0:01:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请来我们公同看看这影片吧\N附上照片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.13,0:01:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,社长和秘书的色情影片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.13,0:01:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被公司内部的川口君发现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.94,0:01:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫我们马上回信的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.94,0:01:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们希望他一定把那个影片带到公司
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.41,0:01:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了看影片 我们前往他们公司取材
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.55,0:01:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好\N你好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.02,0:01:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思，让你特地来一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.69,0:01:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到了和你联系的邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.90,0:01:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,写了很多\N是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.30,0:01:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对那个话题也很感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.97,0:02:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.64,0:02:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你公司
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.38,0:02:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是公司内的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.39,0:02:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公司，是什么样的公司?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.52,0:02:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做什感的\N经营网络的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.73,0:02:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在网上做报告什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.93,0:02:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主要是网络商务\N是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.67,0:02:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 是哪个公司的?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.61,0:02:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秘书?社长?\N秘书和社长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.08,0:02:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.41,0:02:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，在公司内也经常有关于他们的传言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.02,0:02:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我们公司的\N是啊，和社长一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.36,0:02:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.56,0:02:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在公司内也传的沸沸扬扬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.36,0:02:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还被发现了影片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.90,0:03:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是偶然发现的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是偶然发现的 逐渐的传言就扩散了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.17,0:03:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要赶快看一下\N有吗?是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.11,0:03:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.33,0:03:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.87,0:03:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就摸了啊\N因为，已经很硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.47,0:03:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为弥穿这样的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.81,0:03:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直就这样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.48,0:03:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.64,0:04:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样摸了我好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.18,0:04:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边也敏感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.25,0:04:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什么都知道啊\N社长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.66,0:04:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想我怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.93,0:04:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想玩弄社长的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.34,0:04:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很喜欢啊\N因为
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,社长是很好的身材吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.48,0:04:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:05:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.98,0:05:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乳头这么硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样舔了\N谁的都会很硬的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.46,0:05:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以按照喜欢这样做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像这样\N是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.27,0:05:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想我这样吮吸吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.01,0:06:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要\N那看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.29,0:06:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒这睡大了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.63,0:06:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太属害了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的好大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.18,0:06:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么敏感了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.05,0:06:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的肉棒也好大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的好大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.94,0:06:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也来摸我的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.07,0:07:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.48,0:07:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里吗?\N是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.55,0:07:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.82,0:07:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,社长的肉棒好硬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.03,0:07:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,碰到我的屁股上面了\N称自己碰过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.10,0:07:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为这题硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.84,0:07:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,社长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好爽,不行，好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.25,0:07:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里很敏感
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.27,0:08:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很快变硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.01,0:08:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样捏住了\N当然很硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.48,0:08:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要继续吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.02,0:08:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续?\N是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.49,0:08:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,社长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.91,0:08:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小穴也很热了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.05,0:08:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也来摸我的小穴\N还不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.65,0:08:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想我做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经摸了"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.15,0:09:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那边也是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.76,0:09:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也摸小穴了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.50,0:09:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确认一下吧\N确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.04,0:09:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.04,0:09:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.59,0:10:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好摸那里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.20,0:10:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是摸就可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.53,0:10:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摸一下，来舔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.48,0:10:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请给我看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要看吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.62,0:10:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想我看吧?\N看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.77,0:10:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弥在我的桌子上做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:11:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想我怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小穴，很湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.39,0:11:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也来舔小穴的洞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.06,0:11:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真没辨法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.35,0:11:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服，好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.75,0:11:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阴蒂好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行,不行，去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.18,0:12:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.32,0:12:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发出那么淫荡的声音了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.46,0:12:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事,我的小穴好热
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.53,0:12:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个也知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.40,0:12:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都知道，那里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.01,0:12:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下面湿湿的\N是的,很湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.64,0:13:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忍不住了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.44,0:13:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样插满的话\N怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.31,0:13:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.19,0:13:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.53,0:13:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很兴奋了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.14,0:13:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想要\N在我的桌子上面做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.21,0:13:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想多做点淫荡的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.62,0:13:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.96,0:14:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自己那么舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.96,0:14:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还想要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.90,0:14:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.56,0:14:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.70,0:14:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.97,0:14:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.23,0:14:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.97,0:14:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.90,0:14:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.10,0:14:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.97,0:14:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒这么大了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.18,0:14:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太喜欢你了\N就勃起了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.32,0:14:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好变态
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.59,0:14:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想舔吗?\N当然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.47,0:14:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也看这
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.34,0:14:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样被看很舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.48,0:14:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.42,0:14:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再好好看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.23,0:15:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真美味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.70,0:15:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,社长的真美味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么美味吗\N很美味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蛋蛋也很喜欢吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.30,0:16:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好硬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.31,0:16:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道你在说什么\N不知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.44,0:16:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.33,0:16:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么喜欢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.40,0:16:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想肉棒插进来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.73,0:16:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要吗?\N不行，小穴想要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.34,0:17:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从后面插进来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.55,0:17:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要，从后面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个可以脱下来吧\N是的，脱掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.82,0:17:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赶快的 小穴很想要肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.24,0:17:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,社长,今天的也好大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.57,0:17:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要什么了啊\N想要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.66,0:17:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从后面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.73,0:17:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:17:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全插满我的小穴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.15,0:18:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样?\N是的，好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,插满 很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.63,0:18:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒 插到深处
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.78,0:18:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，社长，好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.85,0:18:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.00,0:19:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.41,0:19:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来，再来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.55,0:19:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,插到深处 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.35,0:19:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,社长的肉棒 插到深处
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.49,0:19:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样？\N是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.37,0:19:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.64,0:19:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想看吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.46,0:20:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.19,0:20:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,墙壁都在晃动\N哪里的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.87,0:20:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒,全插满了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.74,0:20:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.87,0:20:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.61,0:20:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好爽,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.69,0:20:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.22,0:20:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.04,0:20:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.31,0:20:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来，再插进来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.19,0:21:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒，好硬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.87,0:21:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,社长的好激烈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.88,0:21:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.68,0:21:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.50,0:21:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒，好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.32,0:22:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,社长的全插满了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.60,0:22:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是,我也要继续
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.50,0:22:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒，很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.70,0:23:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摸我的屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.91,0:23:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全插满
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.25,0:23:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，去了,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.25,0:23:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.40,0:23:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.34,0:23:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样插满好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.36,0:24:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.58,0:24:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也喜欢那样
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.91,0:24:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.05,0:24:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.26,0:24:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.00,0:24:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来，再来，去了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.95,0:25:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个也不需要了吧\N不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.10,0:25:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想你的插进来
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.57,0:25:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己扒开
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.17,0:25:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,双腿高一点\N好的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.79,0:25:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒，赶快的，想要
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.34,0:25:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.28,0:26:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.48,0:26:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒好硬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.63,0:26:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去了,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.30,0:26:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.63,0:26:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去了，插满了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.51,0:26:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.78,0:26:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?\N肉棒插满小穴
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.39,0:26:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好看一下\N看一下肉棒插满的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.88,0:27:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.68,0:27:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里，好棒,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.76,0:27:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，去了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.77,0:27:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按照喜欢那样做
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.11,0:27:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按照喜欢那样插满
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.44,0:27:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,金插满
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.59,0:27:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，去了，好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.33,0:27:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.27,0:28:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去了,不行，去了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.85,0:28:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来，按照社长喜欢的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.92,0:28:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.00,0:29:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜欢骑乘位
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.08,0:29:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好爽，真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.22,0:29:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来，插进来
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.83,0:29:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，去了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.19,0:30:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样不行
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.33,0:30:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样不行
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.21,0:30:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，好激烈
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.54,0:30:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,社长,好激烈
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.97,0:30:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全插满了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.70,0:30:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都看到了\N看到了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.84,0:30:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.25,0:31:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我离不开肉棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.14,0:31:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样不行
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.82,0:31:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真舒服，好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.22,0:31:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.56,0:31:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去了,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.89,0:31:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.31,0:32:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢那样
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.65,0:32:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己抽送\N可以
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.86,0:32:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光社长自己动
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.26,0:32:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.20,0:32:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.07,0:32:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,插满 真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.01,0:32:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，去了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.22,0:32:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，去了,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.65,0:33:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好硬，这个肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.32,0:33:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全插进来
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.06,0:33:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里,不行,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.53,0:33:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，去了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.60,0:33:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.23,0:34:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢的插到深处
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.39,0:34:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赶快的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.80,0:34:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.67,0:34:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,激烈一点
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.68,0:34:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.28,0:35:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,子宫的深处\N插进来
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.50,0:35:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.17,0:35:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.50,0:35:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，去了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.45,0:35:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.86,0:35:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还想要吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.79,0:35:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能插进去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.81,0:36:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.28,0:36:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来摸，好好摸一下
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.36,0:36:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.23,0:36:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小穴的深处 肉棒全插满
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.84,0:36:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，去了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.25,0:36:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里不行,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.85,0:36:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.33,0:36:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高潮了几次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.87,0:36:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.34,0:37:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要社长的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.68,0:37:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的?射出来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.28,0:37:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘴里，射到我的嘴里
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.75,0:37:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,社长的精液\N射到我的嘴里
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.30,0:37:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射出来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.19,0:37:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射了好多好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.60,0:38:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射了好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.40,0:38:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.55,0:38:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.02,0:38:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射到嘴里的怎么了?\N全喝掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.30,0:38:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真美味
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.43,0:38:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.50,0:38:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.44,0:38:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，光想和社长做爱的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.05,0:38:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也想公司的事情了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.85,0:38:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有想\N真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.86,0:38:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有,性爱
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.19,0:39:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.66,0:39:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的脑海里光是那些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.87,0:39:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,性爱，肉棒 精液
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.07,0:39:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这些
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.67,0:39:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.88,0:39:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.49,0:39:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惊愕于影片内秘书的淫荡
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.36,0:39:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不只是接待 秘书自己也很享受性爱
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.43,0:39:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们再次拜托了川口
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.10,0:39:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尝试着和秘书接触进行取材
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.57,0:39:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这边\N好的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.51,0:39:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.71,0:39:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好\N你好，我是社长的秘书
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.32,0:40:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,这是我的名片
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.66,0:40:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的，不好意忠\N谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.93,0:40:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,川口的介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.67,0:40:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才来这里进行拍摄的\N是的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.01,0:40:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.34,0:40:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想多聊一下\N可以一起拍照吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.41,0:40:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.68,0:40:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的，没事 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.21,0:40:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.22,0:40:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感谢祢配合我们的取材
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.35,0:40:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才是，谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.22,0:40:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次，做为特辑
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.50,0:40:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.10,0:40:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,网络商务的最先端企业
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.63,0:40:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有很多想问的\N好的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.97,0:40:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.77,0:40:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先我想问的 你好年轻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.78,0:40:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.45,0:41:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.18,0:41:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.45,0:41:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在几岁\N我现在26岁
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.05,0:41:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.85,0:41:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好年轻啊\N谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.59,0:41:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,双腿也这么漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.66,0:41:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.27,0:41:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到了 没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.34,0:41:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个纽扣\N但是一直都这样
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.28,0:41:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.82,0:41:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好大胆的公司
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.56,0:41:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.96,0:41:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以按照自己喜欢的那样穿
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.69,0:41:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N是的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.30,0:41:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桐岛是社长秘书吧？\N是的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.37,0:42:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,社长秘书
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.91,0:42:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平时都做什么工作呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.84,0:42:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 社长的日程管理
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.12,0:42:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有一起去客服那边
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.99,0:42:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.72,0:42:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃饭也要一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.59,0:42:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 在一起的时间比较长
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.13,0:42:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.93,0:42:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N是的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.33,0:42:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.73,0:42:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.73,0:42:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要很会照顾社长吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.54,0:42:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.94,0:42:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 尽可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.54,0:42:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.88,0:42:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么经常一起外出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.48,0:42:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.15,0:42:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 都会一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.15,0:42:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.49,0:42:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N是的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.49,0:42:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.02,0:42:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他的 前面的话就到那里\N好的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.89,0:42:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不也有其他社长的朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.03,0:43:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样的 会议之类的\N不是有很多应酬吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.90,0:43:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去喝酒的话
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.97,0:43:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桐岛你不是很漂亮很年轻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.38,0:43:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上的活动
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.59,0:43:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是怎样的？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.66,0:43:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全不会\N是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.13,0:43:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和社长
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.80,0:43:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会有那样的关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.27,0:43:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,社长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.94,0:43:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保密\N保密啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.28,0:43:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保密的话 该不会
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.68,0:43:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.09,0:43:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会有这样的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.16,0:43:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我是不会撒谎的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.29,0:44:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.03,0:44:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 有的话
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.90,0:44:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也会顺从
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.57,0:44:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这么年轻 周末的时候公司休息吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.11,0:44:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会去很多的地方玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.59,0:44:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,休息的时候我基本在家里
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.39,0:44:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很享受在职场
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.59,0:44:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,社长不也是男人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.80,0:44:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个 也有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.53,0:44:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？\N我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.54,0:44:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.61,0:44:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你也说拍摄的事情了\N是的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.08,0:44:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,川口
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.42,0:45:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我传了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.09,0:45:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个影片
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.76,0:45:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.76,0:45:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个\N这个是你吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.43,0:45:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.70,0:45:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.44,0:45:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把那个影片传给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.64,0:45:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 川口
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.25,0:45:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊\N是的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.39,0:45:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个真的是桐岛弥吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.06,0:45:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.26,0:45:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这确实是我
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.67,0:45:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.94,0:45:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.07,0:45:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到看了这个\N倒没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.47,0:45:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暴露了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.61,0:45:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个，完全
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.75,0:46:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弥很喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.55,0:46:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很喜欢的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.29,0:46:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看了这个\N是啊，很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.16,0:46:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和社长一直在做
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.10,0:46:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都直接说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.70,0:46:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.50,0:46:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?\N是的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.51,0:46:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事，没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.11,0:46:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也听说了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.51,0:46:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公司不是有很多男生吗?\N不会想要
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.12,0:46:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.92,0:46:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总有很多男人来我们公司
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.39,0:46:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以感受到他们的视线
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.86,0:46:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会很想要
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.60,0:47:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,社长不是很帅气吗\N是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.27,0:47:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会自己很主动吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.41,0:47:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也有那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.35,0:47:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.28,0:47:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜欢自己主动出击
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.55,0:47:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也都看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.29,0:47:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看了吧?\N那聊起来就快了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.43,0:47:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么在这个公司
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.03,0:47:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对方只是和社长吗?\N是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.64,0:47:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很微妙的\N好像还有
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.84,0:47:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.64,0:47:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公司里面有坏员工
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.85,0:47:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们会希望被凌辱
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.12,0:47:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个心情也是
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.39,0:47:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不喜欢被动\N所以不只是和社长
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.66,0:48:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，那也有忍耐的成分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.27,0:48:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的,会忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.81,0:48:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.54,0:48:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚开始
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.21,0:48:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.95,0:48:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没摸吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.29,0:48:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是没摸
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.49,0:48:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为 这个抽摄的话
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.76,0:48:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.90,0:48:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我拿来了好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.77,0:48:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.44,0:48:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在包里，这个
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.18,0:48:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个知道吗?\N我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.59,0:48:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请打开开关
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.40,0:49:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很始的振动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.60,0:49:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,碰到很多的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.20,0:49:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赶快的
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.74,0:49:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什题拿着这个
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.08,0:49:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我收到了情报
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.02,0:49:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觉得弥会喜欢\N真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.96,0:49:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.50,0:49:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想拍摄一下
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.97,0:49:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.85,0:49:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在工作
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.59,0:50:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发出馨音的话会被听到
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.13,0:50:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.13,0:51:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.20,0:51:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.01,0:51:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.92,0:52:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.46,0:52:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样好棒，好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.88,0:52:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.09,0:52:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，去了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.30,0:52:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去了 去了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.86,0:53:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好大胆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.53,0:53:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我忘记还在拍摄了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.60,0:53:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是会议室
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.67,0:53:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要保密\N真的好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.01,0:53:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以脱下来吗\N一定
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.88,0:53:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不需要袜子了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.76,0:54:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚开始就很想知道\N是的
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.64,0:54:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒的类型啊\N很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.44,0:54:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个就是胸围
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.11,0:54:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尺码是多少
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.78,0:54:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.45,0:54:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有罩杯吧\N是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.46,0:54:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒，这么近距离的看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.80,0:54:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以看\N可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.53,0:54:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.47,0:54:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乳头出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.68,0:54:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有这么淫荡的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.88,0:54:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以吗?\N完全0K
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.09,0:55:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧\N是的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.82,0:55:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不够 还可以继续吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.43,0:55:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下面湿湿的了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.11,0:55:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是振动棒的话\N还不够吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.58,0:55:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是振动棒的话
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.45,0:55:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.19,0:55:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有一根?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.39,0:55:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.26,0:55:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿来了好厉害的\N知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.00,0:55:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道吧？\N是的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.27,0:55:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我家也有\N也有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.14,0:55:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢吗\N喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.41,0:56:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的不一棣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.49,0:56:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很糟糕\N没事，没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.56,0:56:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是取材\N大家会安静的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.03,0:56:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会听到吧?\N没事
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.83,0:56:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会议室在二楼\N那没事
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.58,0:56:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想再好好爽一下
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.38,0:56:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.77,0:57:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 湿湿的
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.36,0:58:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.49,0:58:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.89,0:58:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来，再来
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.37,0:58:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.84,0:58:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.25,0:58:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真爽
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.60,0:59:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.15,0:59:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.35,0:59:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.89,0:59:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以再使用一个吗?\N再一个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.57,0:59:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是一个不够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.10,0:59:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不够
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.64,0:59:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再好好刺激一下
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.39,1:00:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.48,1:00:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.16,1:00:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.11,1:01:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，深处去了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.05,1:01:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，去了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.20,1:01:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.48,1:01:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.28,1:01:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你带来了这样的
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.42,1:01:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒的反应\N糟糕
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.63,1:01:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很喜欢吗\N好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.17,1:01:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.91,1:02:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吓到我了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.65,1:02:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.45,1:02:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，我太热衷了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.59,1:02:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的好淫荡啊\N是的
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.40,1:02:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么淫荡的话
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.80,1:02:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.34,1:02:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.61,1:02:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被暴露的话很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.54,1:02:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的?\N真的吗
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.21,1:02:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也把这个摄影机给你
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.28,1:02:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你来拍一下
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.35,1:02:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好呢，那很好
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.76,1:02:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.43,1:02:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.57,1:03:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,邀请了影片提供者川口进行AV拍摄
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.04,1:03:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后天
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.17,1:03:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在没有员工的休息日 让我们一起同行
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.25,1:03:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在\N在呢
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.92,1:03:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过去吧\N好的，过去吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.53,1:03:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,川口\N桐岛，怎么了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.26,1:03:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.80,1:03:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你工作辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.14,1:03:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这都是我分内的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.48,1:03:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好伟大
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.42,1:03:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.09,1:03:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看了我的影片\N自慰了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.16,1:04:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都知道
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.77,1:04:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个误解了吧?\N误解
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.70,1:04:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,误解什么
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.37,1:04:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.51,1:04:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,背着我做了那样的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.18,1:04:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要做什么
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.59,1:04:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己自慰了吧?\N我没有
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.46,1:04:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都知道的
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.60,1:04:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定搞错了\N搞错了？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.20,1:04:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都知道
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.14,1:04:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之后就可以了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.41,1:04:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.48,1:04:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是怎么做的
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.69,1:05:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么做
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.16,1:05:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说不出来\N现在没人
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.76,1:05:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个\N休息日出勤
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.84,1:05:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没人在的
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.84,1:05:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下\N好棒的领带
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.25,1:05:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢什么游戏
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.12,1:05:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢这样吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.79,1:05:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.47,1:05:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.74,1:05:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被绑的心情
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.54,1:05:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢这样的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.48,1:06:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.55,1:06:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜不喜欢 问一下肉棒吧
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.70,1:06:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很冷吗
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.24,1:06:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很敏感，勃起了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.65,1:06:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都看到了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.72,1:06:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.72,1:06:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平时总偷拍
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.33,1:06:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己看自慰
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.53,1:06:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天实际被摸了怎么样
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.14,1:07:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是幻想乳头就勃起了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.14,1:07:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好变态啊
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.82,1:07:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己知道吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.09,1:07:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒很硬了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.36,1:07:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想我摸的话就说一下
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.97,1:07:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么想摸我的身体
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.78,1:07:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忍不住了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.32,1:07:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也想亲吻了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.59,1:07:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想亲吻了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.20,1:08:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舌头伸出来了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.74,1:08:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想亲吻的话
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.08,1:08:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝掉我的口水
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.08,1:08:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全喝掉
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.56,1:08:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样?味道
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.56,1:08:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甜吗?想要吧
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.36,1:08:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢这样吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.11,1:08:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.72,1:08:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.25,1:08:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很厉害吗
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.12,1:08:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到我和社长做爱 自慰了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.69,1:09:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发出謦音了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.96,1:09:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还夹住我
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.83,1:09:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更想我舔吗
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.10,1:09:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求我 说请再舔一下
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.44,1:09:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请再舔一下\N说了啊，变态
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.47,1:10:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说了那样的话\N肉棒糟糕
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.07,1:10:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看一下
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.74,1:10:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己知道吧
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.55,1:10:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想我赶快摸\N舔一下吧
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.43,1:10:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汗臬味
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.83,1:10:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很努力工作了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.11,1:10:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想我怎么故呢?肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.65,1:11:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样说我不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.12,1:11:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想我怎么故
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.26,1:11:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒想我怎么做\N胸部就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.93,1:11:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想舔吗?\N舌头那样伸出来
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.27,1:11:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思\N好变态啊
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.23,1:11:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想舔吧？\N舌头伸如来
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.23,1:11:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.57,1:11:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么想要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.97,1:12:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊\N看了变态的影片
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.05,1:12:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这么硬了了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.98,1:12:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在也没人
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.72,1:12:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赶快脱下来啊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.87,1:12:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.07,1:12:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒出来了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.55,1:12:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可爱的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.69,1:12:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么摸舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.83,1:12:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.83,1:12:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想我赶快舔一下吗
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.44,1:13:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的口水 肉棒湿湿的了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.11,1:13:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒出来了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.19,1:13:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龟头湿湿的了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.39,1:13:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想什么
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.68,1:13:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很硬了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.95,1:13:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在发抖的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.55,1:13:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想我抽送吗
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.42,1:13:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像这样
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.89,1:14:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢这样吗
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.83,1:14:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想我摸吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.30,1:14:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢啊\N好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.71,1:14:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么硬了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.38,1:14:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒，看一下
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.26,1:14:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更加硬了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.22,1:15:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直接摸舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.70,1:15:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.58,1:15:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.58,1:15:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的肉棒很硬了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.06,1:15:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蛋蛋也很硬了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.99,1:15:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近什么时候射精的
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.46,1:15:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天?今天?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.33,1:15:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.20,1:15:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那今天堆积了很多吧
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.14,1:15:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.01,1:15:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平时都只是自慰吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.55,1:16:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看了我的影片
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.49,1:16:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光自慰了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.36,1:16:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蛋蛋好硬
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.14,1:16:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒在发抖
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.34,1:17:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只是舔蛋蛋\N也舔肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.08,1:17:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想我舔吧
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.48,1:17:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想我舔肉棒吧
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.96,1:17:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想我舔的话
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.36,1:17:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不说的话不舔哦
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.97,1:17:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想我舔哪里
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.64,1:17:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到深处
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.38,1:17:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到深处?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.18,1:17:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好奢侈啊
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.22,1:18:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.76,1:18:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,深处这样被舔\N好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.78,1:18:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好硬
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.05,1:18:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.65,1:18:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像这样
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.19,1:19:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想我这样舔吧
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.13,1:19:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很喜欢这样吧
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.00,1:19:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么快速吮吸的话
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.68,1:19:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.82,1:19:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都含住吗
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.02,1:19:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.36,1:19:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.23,1:19:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.00,1:20:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看一下
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.67,1:20:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射了这么多到我的嘴里
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.15,1:20:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请好好的努力工作哦
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.24,1:20:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我的摄影机里面\N还有员工凌辱她的画面
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.25,1:21:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,社长
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.78,1:21:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要做什么
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.32,1:21:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直用淫荡的眼神看着我吧
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.79,1:21:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有\N不是吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.40,1:21:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都感受到了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.27,1:21:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真实说一下
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.14,1:21:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是不是那样吧
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.14,1:21:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢吧
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.02,1:21:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都知道
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.49,1:21:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直可以感受到你的视线
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.03,1:21:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮你做这样的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.64,1:22:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疼吗\N哪里都疼
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.44,1:22:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是第一次做吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.26,1:22:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.66,1:22:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是那个表情吧
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.53,1:22:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再看一次\N刚刚看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.47,1:22:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光说谎,来这边
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.42,1:22:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.49,1:22:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧?怎么可能往手
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.63,1:22:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脸上都写着“请做吧”
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.43,1:22:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.23,1:23:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.51,1:23:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想我做这样的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.85,1:23:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.32,1:23:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全不是那样的表情
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.73,1:23:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿着这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.80,1:23:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.07,1:23:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢我这样摸肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.81,1:23:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉大家吧
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.03,1:24:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.10,1:24:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好热
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.64,1:24:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直在看我的胸部吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.92,1:24:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还想再继续吧
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.25,1:24:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直那个眼神看我吧
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.72,1:24:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想胸部碰远去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.73,1:24:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.87,1:24:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想看乳头吧
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.55,1:24:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直在看
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.29,1:25:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先给我看一下肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.30,1:25:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可爱的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.91,1:25:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.11,1:25:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?住手
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.91,1:25:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说完全佳手
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.92,1:25:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该说请继续做吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.66,1:25:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒很热了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.48,1:26:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒很大了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.82,1:26:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.49,1:26:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.70,1:26:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服\N总用淫荡的眼神看我
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.43,1:26:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工作做得不好
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.90,1:26:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光在想这样的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.05,1:26:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想看胸部吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.80,1:26:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用胸部
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.20,1:26:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胸部，手不行
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.60,1:26:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要摸，我来摸肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.14,1:27:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒被胸部摸了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.50,1:27:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒很大了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.18,1:27:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用我的口水,湿湿的
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.45,1:27:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,湿湿的肉棒，一直
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.46,1:27:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胸部怎么样
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.66,1:27:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样夹住肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.73,1:27:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.87,1:28:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腰部抬趋来
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.15,1:28:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用胸部帮你夹住
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.83,1:28:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒很热了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.71,1:28:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很硬了，肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.84,1:28:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龟头,很硬了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.25,1:28:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么硬了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.33,1:29:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还想要吧
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.47,1:29:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么做?这样吗
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.29,1:29:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这里被口交的心情怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.76,1:29:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都含住了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.78,1:29:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好大
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.87,1:30:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都在发抖
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.72,1:31:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好大，好硬
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.48,1:31:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.22,1:31:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.31,1:32:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射了这么多
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.86,1:32:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个事情要保密
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.39,1:32:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次再继续吧
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.80,1:32:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.42,1:32:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到这个影片的我们
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.82,1:32:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又接到了她的联击
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.76,1:32:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天怎么了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.03,1:32:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.30,1:32:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫来了员工
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.37,1:33:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想今天再做一下
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.04,1:33:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要做吗?\N就在那边
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.04,1:33:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.51,1:33:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧\N出发，好期待
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.52,1:33:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,川口
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.60,1:33:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天也做吧
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.27,1:33:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又要吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.20,1:33:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天要拍摄
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.08,1:33:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢吧?\N被拍
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.68,1:33:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.35,1:33:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还说不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.49,1:33:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很喜欢吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.96,1:33:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像这样的
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.69,1:34:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天要做什么
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.17,1:34:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都摸了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.71,1:34:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被摸好兴奋
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.11,1:34:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.25,1:34:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样不行\N道歉什么?我还什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.59,1:34:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要做什么
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.46,1:34:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想我打吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.53,1:34:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想我打吗?今天\N不是
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.60,1:34:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.41,1:34:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的手很舒服吧?\N像这样被打
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.55,1:35:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被打
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.62,1:35:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样被打，很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.36,1:35:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乳头很硬了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.50,1:35:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在看哪里？\N看我的胸部了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.30,1:35:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没看\N我感受到视线了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.98,1:35:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真实的回答\N我没着，真的?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.05,1:35:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说谎的话，我会继续做的
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.92,1:35:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想被玩弄吧
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.66,1:35:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天也要你全裸
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.74,1:35:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请住手\N不是往手吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.01,1:35:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反应那么好
Dialogue: 0,1:35:59.08,1:36:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总加班\N要工作到什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.82,1:36:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.42,1:36:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.63,1:36:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样不行
Dialogue: 0,1:36:16.43,1:36:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直都做吧
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.30,1:36:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个内裤也不需要了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:33.51,1:36:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在办公室你全裸了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.26,1:36:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.06,1:36:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在发抖
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.40,1:36:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想我摸吗
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.74,1:36:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请转到后面
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.88,1:37:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好疼\N疼吗
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.28,1:37:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该是很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.96,1:37:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乳头很硬了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.16,1:37:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屁股被打，乳头很硬了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:37:29.70,1:37:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个身体，好变态啊
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.58,1:37:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到胸部了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.78,1:37:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐下来看一下
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.79,1:37:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想看我脱下来的样子吧
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.59,1:37:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么淫荡的眼神
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.06,1:38:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有用那样的眼神看\N其他员工吧
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.88,1:38:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很喜欢我的屁股吧
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.82,1:38:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很想摸吧
Dialogue: 0,1:38:26.43,1:38:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不行
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.36,1:38:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还没说可以摸
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.50,1:38:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么一直在遮掩肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.10,1:38:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒勃起了吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.91,1:38:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没勃起吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.84,1:38:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒没勃起?\N我在这里肉棒没勃起?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.78,1:38:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样不行
Dialogue: 0,1:38:51.79,1:38:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很期待吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.74,1:39:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好亲吻一下
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.94,1:39:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢我的嘴吧
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.01,1:39:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,张开嘴
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.23,1:39:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.84,1:39:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.71,1:39:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乳头一直很硬
Dialogue: 0,1:40:07.86,1:40:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想摸胸部吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.47,1:40:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么，脱下来
Dialogue: 0,1:40:17.87,1:40:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手不是在发抖吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.34,1:40:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不赶快脱下来的话
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.88,1:40:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会玩弄很多地方的
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.62,1:40:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抽送肉棒了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.09,1:40:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想舔这里吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.83,1:40:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想舔胸部吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.18,1:41:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看一下
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.59,1:41:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好大,想舔吧
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.73,1:41:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求我一下
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.67,1:41:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请让我舔一下\N真没办法
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.88,1:41:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来
Dialogue: 0,1:41:47.43,1:41:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦吗\N很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:42:07.71,1:42:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很热了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.12,1:42:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己在抽送啊
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.12,1:42:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看着我的屁股 好好抽送一下
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.74,1:42:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,1:42:34.41,1:42:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想摸吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.21,1:42:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那摸一下 我的屁股
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.56,1:42:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像这样摸肉棒很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.71,1:43:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好热
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.24,1:43:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的屁股好热
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.19,1:43:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒好热
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.26,1:43:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胸部也很热
Dialogue: 0,1:43:32.07,1:43:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像这样被胸部夹住很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:43:52.09,1:43:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘴就在这里哦\N我的嘴
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.43,1:44:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.57,1:44:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想被我的嘴舔吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:10.90,1:44:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想我舔吧
Dialogue: 0,1:44:45.34,1:44:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒，好硬
Dialogue: 0,1:45:22.71,1:45:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光你自己爽好狡猾
Dialogue: 0,1:45:27.38,1:45:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来请帮我爽一下
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.39,1:45:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来这边
Dialogue: 0,1:45:51.67,1:45:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前面有小穴哦
Dialogue: 0,1:45:59.95,1:46:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样?\N舔一下
Dialogue: 0,1:46:07.96,1:46:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好舔,用舌头
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.70,1:46:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:46:44.93,1:46:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好热，很热
Dialogue: 0,1:46:57.34,1:46:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好热
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.94,1:47:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,1:47:04.68,1:47:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样不行，看一下
Dialogue: 0,1:47:09.48,1:47:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要插进来的地方，看一下
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.30,1:47:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很兴奋码?自己套弄肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:47:33.64,1:47:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想看小穴吧?\N想看吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:38.58,1:47:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想看吗?好好看一下
Dialogue: 0,1:47:42.98,1:47:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很漂亮\N漂亮吗
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.79,1:47:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那舔干净 再舔干净一点
Dialogue: 0,1:48:01.27,1:48:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服，好好舔一下阴蒂
Dialogue: 0,1:48:08.88,1:48:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:13.15,1:48:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:48:17.95,1:48:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好用舌头
Dialogue: 0,1:48:24.36,1:48:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:48:38.51,1:48:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再快速的，再继续
Dialogue: 0,1:48:48.92,1:48:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，去了
Dialogue: 0,1:49:00.79,1:49:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是淫荡的文迪吧
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.67,1:49:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你帮我爽
Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.27,1:49:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也帮你爽\N翘起来
Dialogue: 0,1:49:18.81,1:49:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么害羞的姿势
Dialogue: 0,1:49:23.48,1:49:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屁股转过来
Dialogue: 0,1:49:27.22,1:49:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全看到了
Dialogue: 0,1:49:30.96,1:49:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屁眼也是
Dialogue: 0,1:49:34.96,1:49:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样被舔的话很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:49:39.23,1:49:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:43.50,1:49:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请赶快回答
Dialogue: 0,1:50:21.01,1:50:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又自己抽送了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:50:24.75,1:50:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么喜欢自己的肉棒啊
Dialogue: 0,1:50:31.42,1:50:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超变态
Dialogue: 0,1:50:35.82,1:50:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮你舔 转到这边
Dialogue: 0,1:50:42.90,1:50:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?肉棒\N抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:50:59.45,1:51:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好多汗水
Dialogue: 0,1:51:14.80,1:51:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:16.53,1:51:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 在插进来之前\N要忍耐一下
Dialogue: 0,1:51:22.80,1:51:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:42.56,1:51:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心情如何
Dialogue: 0,1:51:46.43,1:51:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:51.77,1:51:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢激烈的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:52:06.58,1:52:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再帮你爽一下
Dialogue: 0,1:52:12.59,1:52:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,躺下来
Dialogue: 0,1:52:19.26,1:52:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屁眼全看到了
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.60,1:52:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么发出奇怪的声音
Dialogue: 0,1:52:39.15,1:52:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舔小穴的同时抽送肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:53:07.84,1:53:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛苦
Dialogue: 0,1:53:11.04,1:53:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢吧
Dialogue: 0,1:53:23.19,1:53:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要吧?想把肉棒插进来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:53:30.40,1:53:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己插进来
Dialogue: 0,1:53:32.53,1:53:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想插到小穴里面吧
Dialogue: 0,1:53:43.48,1:53:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,1:53:48.42,1:53:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服\N舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:59.63,1:54:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服吧?像这样抽送的话
Dialogue: 0,1:54:12.97,1:54:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来,再来
Dialogue: 0,1:54:17.51,1:54:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要帮我高潮
Dialogue: 0,1:54:26.72,1:54:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服\N舒服吗?忍耐一下
Dialogue: 0,1:54:37.40,1:54:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，去了
Dialogue: 0,1:54:54.08,1:54:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很硬的肉棒\N插到我的小穴里面了
Dialogue: 0,1:55:09.96,1:55:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从这边插进来
Dialogue: 0,1:55:18.51,1:55:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒插满
Dialogue: 0,1:55:30.25,1:55:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒插进来 到我的小穴里面
Dialogue: 0,1:55:35.59,1:55:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不插进来的话
Dialogue: 0,1:55:38.93,1:55:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手指都进来了
Dialogue: 0,1:55:46.40,1:55:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒再硬一点
Dialogue: 0,1:55:51.87,1:55:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小穴湿湿的了
Dialogue: 0,1:56:02.95,1:56:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赶快插进来
Dialogue: 0,1:56:31.11,1:56:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,1:56:39.79,1:56:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:56:42.59,1:56:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，去了
Dialogue: 0,1:56:45.66,1:56:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去了，去了
Dialogue: 0,1:57:02.21,1:57:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小穴很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:57:07.41,1:57:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,插到湿湿的小穴里面\N肉棒很热了
Dialogue: 0,1:57:20.63,1:57:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来舔
Dialogue: 0,1:57:25.70,1:57:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都舔干净
Dialogue: 0,1:57:38.51,1:57:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己弄得湿湿的
Dialogue: 0,1:57:43.18,1:57:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乳头被玩弄了
Dialogue: 0,1:58:01.34,1:58:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想插进去了\N想要了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:58:05.61,1:58:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都很硬了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:58:41.11,1:58:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己抽送一下
Dialogue: 0,1:58:43.11,1:58:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想插进去\N想插进来吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:58:46.98,1:58:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很喜欢小穴吧？\N好孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:58:52.05,1:58:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很喜欢小穴\N好孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:59:00.73,1:59:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己插进来
Dialogue: 0,1:59:09.54,1:59:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想插到这里吧
Dialogue: 0,1:59:22.48,1:59:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大肉棒插进来了
Dialogue: 0,1:59:27.96,1:59:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想我这样做吧
Dialogue: 0,1:59:33.69,1:59:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来好好摸我
Dialogue: 0,1:59:38.77,1:59:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屁股也是
Dialogue: 0,1:59:42.24,1:59:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:59:45.97,1:59:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐一下 到我高潮为止
Dialogue: 0,1:59:51.45,1:59:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，去了
Dialogue: 0,2:00:03.06,2:00:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想高潮吧?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:07.33,2:00:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,躺下来
Dialogue: 0,2:00:19.61,2:00:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,2:00:19.74,2:00:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再插进去
Dialogue: 0,2:00:22.68,2:00:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想我插到小穴里面吧
Dialogue: 0,2:00:25.61,2:00:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎我插进去吗\N怎要吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:31.49,2:00:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒不要拔出去
Dialogue: 0,2:00:49.90,2:00:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么硬了 乳头和肉棒都是
Dialogue: 0,2:01:08.99,2:01:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想插满我的小穴吗?\N插进来
Dialogue: 0,2:01:12.59,2:01:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒插进来\N自己插进来
Dialogue: 0,2:01:32.08,2:01:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,插进来了
Dialogue: 0,2:01:37.42,2:01:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢吧?摸我的胸部
Dialogue: 0,2:01:53.03,2:01:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,2:01:55.44,2:01:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，好硬
Dialogue: 0,2:01:58.11,2:02:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒，深处好棒
Dialogue: 0,2:02:00.24,2:02:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好硬
Dialogue: 0,2:02:03.84,2:02:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，去了
Dialogue: 0,2:02:13.99,2:02:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服\N舒服吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:18.53,2:02:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐了很久吗
Dialogue: 0,2:02:22.66,2:02:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还想继续吧？ 想射出来吧？
Dialogue: 0,2:02:27.33,2:02:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以射出来 想射了吧？
Dialogue: 0,2:02:32.54,2:02:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒 好硬
Dialogue: 0,2:02:38.15,2:02:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒，深处好棒
Dialogue: 0,2:02:42.68,2:02:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射出来
Dialogue: 0,2:02:56.83,2:02:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射出来
Dialogue: 0,2:03:11.65,2:03:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射出来了吗
Dialogue: 0,2:03:41.81,2:03:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射了这么多
Dialogue: 0,2:03:56.22,2:03:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮你全吮吸干净
Dialogue: 0,2:04:16.24,2:04:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看一下
Dialogue: 0,2:04:20.51,2:04:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么闭眼
Dialogue: 0,2:04:25.05,2:04:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,张开嘴 自己尝一下
Dialogue: 0,2:04:29.99,2:04:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,张开嘴
Dialogue: 0,2:04:33.19,2:04:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好打扫一下
Dialogue: 0,2:04:46.67,2:04:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我吃饱了呢
Dialogue: 0,2:04:50.68,2:04:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,2:04:53.35,2:04:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做的很好
Dialogue: 0,2:05:11.63,2:05:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解放了欲望 对于有性欲的凌辱员工们的痴女秘书
Dialogue: 0,2:05:16.17,2:05:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并没有忘记自己社长秘书的身份
Dialogue: 0,2:05:37.92,2:05:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我保密\N擅自和别人做了吧？
Dialogue: 0,2:05:45.67,2:05:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的有反省吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:49.80,2:05:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样不行哦
Dialogue: 0,2:05:53.67,2:05:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,2:05:56.88,2:05:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的有反省啊
Dialogue: 0,2:06:01.15,2:06:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都因行社长才这样了
Dialogue: 0,2:06:06.62,2:06:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我做太多的成果
Dialogue: 0,2:06:09.69,2:06:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，社长的错\N是啊
Dialogue: 0,2:06:15.43,2:06:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那给这些家伙看看吧\N可以吗
Dialogue: 0,2:06:22.24,2:06:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要舔社长的吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:31.45,2:06:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赶快的
Dialogue: 0,2:06:50.13,2:06:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒很硬了
Dialogue: 0,2:06:54.80,2:06:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直想摸吧
Dialogue: 0,2:06:57.60,2:07:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么大的肉棒\N当然很想摸
Dialogue: 0,2:07:10.42,2:07:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请好好看一下
Dialogue: 0,2:07:26.97,2:07:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好喜欢
Dialogue: 0,2:07:32.04,2:07:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢大肉棒吗\N很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,2:07:53.66,2:07:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,社长的好大
Dialogue: 0,2:07:59.40,2:08:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么喜欢啊
Dialogue: 0,2:08:02.47,2:08:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,2:08:02.60,2:08:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好看着
Dialogue: 0,2:08:07.01,2:08:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,2:08:24.49,2:08:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在看吗
Dialogue: 0,2:08:28.10,2:08:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,2:08:33.03,2:08:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在在含住社长的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,2:08:42.38,2:08:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也来摸一下
Dialogue: 0,2:08:47.71,2:08:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说想要的话
Dialogue: 0,2:08:51.59,2:08:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也会考虑的
Dialogue: 0,2:09:00.39,2:09:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在也是，想做吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:05.20,2:09:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒都勃起了
Dialogue: 0,2:09:08.80,2:09:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在眼前被看的话
Dialogue: 0,2:09:12.01,2:09:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被看怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:16.14,2:09:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想摸了
Dialogue: 0,2:09:18.81,2:09:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒很硬了吧？
Dialogue: 0,2:09:23.22,2:09:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很羡慕吧？
Dialogue: 0,2:09:30.96,2:09:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们真的有反省吗\N是的
Dialogue: 0,2:09:37.63,2:09:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么,很特别的
Dialogue: 0,2:09:42.84,2:09:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起做吧\N可以吗?社长
Dialogue: 0,2:09:48.71,2:09:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想做吗\N不是
Dialogue: 0,2:09:54.05,2:09:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么自己主动地脱下来
Dialogue: 0,2:10:04.19,2:10:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赶快的
Dialogue: 0,2:10:07.26,2:10:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勃起的肉棒过来\N忍不住了吧
Dialogue: 0,2:10:11.80,2:10:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是看了表情就知道了
Dialogue: 0,2:10:27.41,2:10:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真美味
Dialogue: 0,2:10:29.28,2:10:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:33.15,2:10:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,称也想要吧\N想要
Dialogue: 0,2:10:37.56,2:10:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全想要
Dialogue: 0,2:10:42.90,2:10:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用双手握住吧
Dialogue: 0,2:10:47.30,2:10:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以握住吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:50.64,2:10:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想握住吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:54.78,2:10:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弄得湿湿的了
Dialogue: 0,2:11:05.59,2:11:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来,肉棒，好棒
Dialogue: 0,2:11:35.48,2:11:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒真不错
Dialogue: 0,2:11:40.55,2:11:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开心吗\N很开心
Dialogue: 0,2:11:44.16,2:11:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒来这边
Dialogue: 0,2:12:25.67,2:12:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒真美味
Dialogue: 0,2:12:35.28,2:12:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好喜欢吻肉棒啊
Dialogue: 0,2:12:46.09,2:12:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很痛苦吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:48.76,2:12:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为，我很喜欢肉棒
Dialogue: 0,2:13:04.24,2:13:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好尝一下\N可以
Dialogue: 0,2:13:08.38,2:13:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部
Dialogue: 0,2:13:42.28,2:13:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样?做这样的事情
Dialogue: 0,2:13:58.83,2:14:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,2:14:02.43,2:14:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,2:14:06.43,2:14:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢吧?这样的事情
Dialogue: 0,2:14:18.31,2:14:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,2:14:22.98,2:14:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这的也想要
Dialogue: 0,2:14:48.88,2:14:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真美味
Dialogue: 0,2:14:59.69,2:15:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也来好好舔我的
Dialogue: 0,2:15:02.36,2:15:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦,想要吗
Dialogue: 0,2:15:06.09,2:15:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,社长那么想要啊
Dialogue: 0,2:15:11.57,2:15:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很美味吧
Dialogue: 0,2:15:22.11,2:15:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很硬了吧
Dialogue: 0,2:15:35.32,2:15:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快速的\N喜欢快速的吧
Dialogue: 0,2:15:47.73,2:15:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒好硬
Dialogue: 0,2:15:56.14,2:15:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,2:15:59.88,2:16:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的好棒
Dialogue: 0,2:16:08.69,2:16:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想射出来了\N想射出来了吗
Dialogue: 0,2:16:13.63,2:16:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要射了哦
Dialogue: 0,2:16:18.43,2:16:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样射了哦
Dialogue: 0,2:16:22.30,2:16:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射了
Dialogue: 0,2:16:48.86,2:16:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样\N好棒
Dialogue: 0,2:16:52.06,2:16:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,社长,射了这么多
Dialogue: 0,2:17:03.28,2:17:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美味吗?\N很美味
Dialogue: 0,2:17:05.81,2:17:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不够
Dialogue: 0,2:17:08.48,2:17:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再给我你的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,2:17:20.23,2:17:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒好硬
Dialogue: 0,2:17:51.46,2:17:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要射了
Dialogue: 0,2:17:54.80,2:17:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要射了吗?\N就那样射出来
Dialogue: 0,2:18:04.67,2:18:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射了
Dialogue: 0,2:18:17.48,2:18:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射出来了
Dialogue: 0,2:18:29.76,2:18:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,2:18:34.70,2:18:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射了这么多啊
Dialogue: 0,2:18:43.24,2:18:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一个肉棒，赶快的
Dialogue: 0,2:19:00.46,2:19:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服\N舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,2:19:09.80,2:19:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己抽送一下
Dialogue: 0,2:19:12.61,2:19:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要射了\N要射了吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:19:14.47,2:19:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射出来\N都射出来
Dialogue: 0,2:19:18.88,2:19:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,2:19:19.01,2:19:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想射到我的脸上吗?\N变态
Dialogue: 0,2:19:23.42,2:19:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射了 射了
Dialogue: 0,2:20:02.39,2:20:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,2:20:12.40,2:20:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,2:20:18.81,2:20:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,2:20:45.77,2:20:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了满足自己的欲望需求
Dialogue: 0,2:20:49.90,2:20:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她今后也会做为痴女秘书 活跃在舞台吧

